  As budget shrinks R (full copy/socket) goes infeasible FIRST; N/P/H (~G/ns)
  survive longer. The band where R=0 but P=1 is partitions raison detre:
  scene exceeds per-socket DRAM -> replication impossible -> partition is the
  only local-data strategy that fits. (Budget is a feasibility model; see PLAN.)

